name: Hand/machine embroidered and hand beaded stripe cushion
description:
This cushion is machine and hand embroidered and also features some hand beadwork.

It is made out of 100% white cotton and measures 50cm x 50cm

name: Black and white insect cushion WITH INTRICATE EMBROIDERY AND BEADWORK
description:
This cushion cover is hand screen printed with a design from one of my original drawings, inspired by the insect world.(print is the same as black and white insect cushion). However this cushion cover
also features two of the butterfly's embellished with hand embroidery and bead work.

The cushion cover is 50cm x 50cm and is made with with water-based inks printed onto optic white cotton.
This cushion could be part of a set with the the other black and white cushions featured in my shop or a beautiful one off piece on its own.
